      m_Calls: []
  m_text: 'The Poland office is a digital circus. Janusz is losing us 150k a minute,
    the CEO is trying to run the entire company from a damn iPad, and half the staff
    is one click away from a ransomware heart attack. I hired you to be the filter
    between us and total collapse.


    If their credentials match the security
    hash and they aren''t trying to start a labor uprising over a Passat 1.9 TDI,
    just give them


    The queue is waiting. Don''t make me fly over there.'
